eval/

# Tauri app — the Docker image only builds ministr-cli, but cargo-chef
# still needs to read every workspace member's Cargo.toml to generate
# the dependency recipe. Keep the crate's manifest + source in context
# and let `cargo build -p ministr-cli` simply not compile ministr-app.
# The large frontend-only artifacts (dist/, node_modules/) are still
# excluded above.
ministr-app/src/
ministr-app/dist/
ministr-app/node_modules/
ministr-app/pnpm-lock.yaml
ministr-app/package.json
ministr-app/tsconfig*.json
ministr-app/vite.config.ts
ministr-app/index.html
